text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/ValueSet/C4BBSupportingInfoType
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-pct/CodeSystem/PCTSupportingInfoType

name: PCTSupportingInfoTypeVS
title: PCT Supporting Info Type Value Set - locally defined for testing purpose; an external FHIR value set will be created through the HL7 Terminology (THO) process to replace this value set
publisher: HL7 International - Financial Management Work Group

contact.name: HL7 International - Financial Management Work Group

description: Codes to specify the type of the supplied supporting information
